OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The parents of a footballer left in a  
OL,6, coma after an unprovoked assault have  
OL,7, been allowed to visit him in hospital. 
OL,9,FDanny Hodgson, 25, who plays for ECU   
OL,10,FJoondalup in Australia, suffered a     
OL,11,Fbrain bleed in Perth last week.        
OL,13,FNicola and Peter Hodgson, from Cleator 
OL,14,FMoor, Cumbria, were granted a visit on 
OL,15,Fcompassionate grounds on Saturday amid 
OL,16,Ftight Covid restrictions.              
OL,18,FThey said they were "eternally         
OL,19,Fgrateful" to those who had made the    
OL,20,Fvisit possible.                        
